V - Type of the view injected into the presenter. Must extends LazyView.
All Implemented Interfaces:
EventHandlerInterface<EventBusWithLookup>, PresenterInterface<V,EventBusWithLookup>
public class LazyXmlPresenter<V extends LazyView>
extends LazyPresenter<V,EventBusWithLookup>

Lazy presenter to use when the event bus is defined thanks to an XML file. It's a lazy presenter where event bus type has been set to automatically match the type of the event bus generated thanks to an XML file.
